[2026-03-13T17:25:55Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MfZgwAbVwzMG3xKWvuDwE1","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Cloche MVP Implementation Plan\n     2→\n     3→> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.\n     4→\n     5→**Goal:** Build a working Cloche MVP — parse workflow DSL, execute steps in Docker containers, report status via gRPC.\n     6→\n     7→**Architecture:** Three Go binaries (cloche, cloched, cloche-agent) with hexagonal architecture. Domain types and DSL parser are the foundation. Build bottom-up: domain -> DSL -> engine -> agent binary -> daemon -> CLI.\n     8→\n     9→**Tech Stack:** Go 1.22+, protobuf/gRPC, Docker SDK, SQLite (via modernc.org/sqlite — pure Go), testify for assertions.\n    10→\n    11→---\n    12→\n    13→## Phase 1: Foundation\n    14→\n    15→### Task 1: Initialize Go Module and Directory Structure\n    16→\n    17→**Files:**\n    18→- Create: `go.mod`\n    19→- Create: `Makefile`\n    20→- Create: `cmd/cloche/main.go`\n    21→- Create: `cmd/cloched/main.go`\n    22→- Create: `cmd/cloche-agent/main.go`\n    23→\n    24→**Step 1: Initialize Go module**\n    25→\n    26→```bash\n    27→cd /home/lucas/workspace/cloche\n    28→go mod init github.com/cloche-dev/cloche\n    29→```\n    30→\n    31→**Step 2: Create directory structure**\n    32→\n    33→```bash\n    34→mkdir -p cmd/cloche cmd/cloched cmd/cloche-agent\n    35→mkdir -p internal/domain internal/ports\n    36→mkdir -p internal/adapters/docker internal/adapters/sqlite\n    37→mkdir -p internal/adapters/grpc internal/adapters/agents/generic\n    38→mkdir -p internal/adapters/agents/claudecode\n    39→mkdir -p internal/dsl internal/engine internal/protocol\n    40→```\n    41→\n    42→**Step 3: Create placeholder mains**\n    43→\n    44→`cmd/cloche/main.go`:\n    45→```go\n    46→package main\n    47→\n    48→func main() {}\n    49→```\n    50→\n    51→`cmd/cloched/main.go`:\n    52→```go\n    53→package main\n    54→\n    55→func main() {}\n    56→```\n    57→\n    58→`cmd/cloche-agent/main.go`:\n    59→```go\n    60→package main\n    61→\n    62→func main() {}\n    63→```\n    64→\n    65→**Step 4: Create Makefile**\n    66→\n    67→```makefile\n    68→.PHONY: build test lint clean\n    69→\n    70→build:\n    71→\tgo build -o bin/cloche ./cmd/cloche\n    72→\tgo build -o bin/cloched ./cmd/cloched\n    73→\tgo build -o bin/cloche-agent ./cmd/cloche-agent\n    74→\n    75→test:\n    76→\tgo test ./... -v\n    77→\n    78→test-short:\n    79→\tgo test ./... -short\n    80→\n    81→lint:\n    82→\tgo vet ./...\n    83→\n    84→clean:\n    85→\trm -rf bin/\n    86→```\n    87→\n    88→**Step 5: Verify build**\n    89→\n    90→```bash\n    91→make build\n    92→```\n    93→Expected: three binaries in `bin/`\n    94→\n    95→**Step 6: Commit**\n    96→\n    97→```bash\n    98→git add -A && git commit -m \"feat: initialize Go module and project structure\"\n    99→```\n   100→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_0118rtZ5YGK1bqAPH91X3aLP","session_id":"baab609c-7354-4992-8237-78467d40b185","uuid":"14c1d814-f63f-4070-b2c7-431381a9ef48"}
