[2026-03-13T17:25:55Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LBTb7Hfw2UGH2iitu9n9nK","type":"tool_result","content":"   200→```\n   201→\n   202→The `location` field is either `\"container\"` or `\"host\"`. Host workflows are parsed from\n   203→`.cloche/host.cloche` and included in the same response.\n   204→\n   205→```\n   206→GET /api/projects/{name}/workflows/{workflow}/steps/{step}/content\n   207→```\n   208→\n   209→Returns the raw content of the prompt file or script for that step (plain text).\n   210→If the value is an inline command string (not a file reference), return it directly.\n   211→\n   212→## Template / file changes\n   213→\n   214→- New template: `templates/project_detail.html`\n   215→- New page registered in `NewHandler`: `\"project_detail\"`\n   216→- New routes registered in `NewHandler` mux\n   217→- Handler struct gains an optional orchestrator interface field (via `HandlerOption`)\n   218→\n   219→## Not in scope\n   220→\n   221→- Editing workflow files from the UI\n   222→- Evolution history of workflow structure (just current state)\n   223→- Persisting concurrency overrides to disk\n   224→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_0118rtZ5YGK1bqAPH91X3aLP","session_id":"baab609c-7354-4992-8237-78467d40b185","uuid":"feeba474-cc5b-4035-96ce-3795e168211b"}
